title: Trust Issues + Ride or Die, TNF Breakdown - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/19
description:
Get ready for Week 7! On today’s fantasy football podcast, rest of season outlooks and current trust levels for a number of players. Plus a preview of Thursday Night Football between the Saints and Cardinals, and a new edition of “Ride or Die!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 19th, 2022.
